text: Md. Shahjahan is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Sirajganj-6. ==Career== Shahjahan was elected to parliament from Sirajganj-6 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1996. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:7th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Md. Shahjahan (Sirajganj politician)
